data.description: Great Location! Don't miss out on this Beautiful 2-Story Home located in Clearview Meadow in Dover. When you enter this home, you will notice the beautiful Bamboo Flooring on the 1st level. Large sized Great Room leading to a  beautiful kitchen. Enjoy those peaceful moments relaxing outside in your backyard that overlooks the Pond. Upstairs has 4 nice size Bedrooms. The Large Owners' Retreat has a Walk in Closet and Owners Bath with Dual Vanity Sinks. Bedrooms 2 & 3 also have a Walk in Closet. Enjoy the efficiency with your Tankless Water Heater and Water Treatment System. Conveniently located on the 2nd Floor is the Laundry. This home is conveniently located close to many Restaurants, Shopping, DAFB and Rte.1. Don't Let This Home Pass You By, Schedule your showing today!
